<li><strong>Enhanced liquidity management: </strong>Ripple&#8217;s payment system includes its native cryptocurrency, XRP, which can be used as a bridge currency for cross-border transactions. This allows banks to optimize their liquidity management by minimizing the need for maintaining various fiat currencies in different correspondent accounts.</li>
